title: Green synthesis and antitumor activity of (E)-diethyl 2-styrylquinoline-3,4-dicarboxylates
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,26820-26828

Hong Zhang, Jianyuan Wang, Cheng Li, Di Zhao, Tianyu Liang, Yang Li
Application of an environmentally benign and non-toxic eutectic mixture DMU/LTA for the green synthesis of (E)-diethyl 2-arylvinylquinoline-3,4-dicarboxylates is described. A preliminary antitumor evaluation was then assayed.
